00:52:35,143 --> 00:52:37,305
and it's such a unique world with its own rules.

761
00:52:38,025 --> 00:52:43,491
That having the players bring in a whole personal history,

762
00:52:44,251 --> 00:52:46,874
it makes it a lot harder to guide them through the narrative.

763
00:52:46,894 --> 00:52:49,477
And also from a strictly technical perspective,

764
00:52:49,517 --> 00:52:53,140
it's a lot easier to have bandwidth for a single person talking at a time

