771
00:53:17,034 --> 00:53:22,756
found in the preview period with this was like a lot of people actually found

772
00:53:22,796 --> 00:53:23,656
it really freeing.

773
00:53:24,076 --> 00:53:30,301
to not have to say things and to be able to, like, it kind of opened them up to take more risks and to participate more

774
00:53:30,361 --> 00:53:35,646
because then they didn't have to, like, worry about saying something clever or something like that.

775
00:53:35,806 --> 00:53:40,570
So, and I know that that's a taste thing, but I've personally found that freeing.

776
00:53:43,332 --> 00:53:46,735
