00:55:28,910 --> 00:55:34,473
We realized that we just kind of had to pare things down in a way, because if it got too muddy,

801
00:55:36,775 --> 00:55:41,818
or if it got too, yeah, if it wasn't efficient, if the gestures weren't efficient enough,

802
00:55:41,858 --> 00:55:47,221
it would start to get muddy and blurry and it would be harder to kind of, it wasn't as legible basically.

803
00:55:49,502 --> 00:56:11,456
